version_description: I've found a few different versions of this song but none of them were in the correct key and some of the chords didn't really transpose correctly.
The interlude is completely rewritten on the chords and sounds much more like the original than the existing chord contributions.
Original tabbed out with the help of this tutorial. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JFimkHUAB8w changed chords and added small transition.
Specific tab from a live version that was recorded in Portland on 7/22/2017. (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ejRjK_akUwY).

performance.name: Live at Moda Center, Portland, OR, 07/22/2017
